{"tid":1748973,"cid":31,"subCid":0,"title":"張建宗，你在網絡上又添上新潮文了！","createTime":"2019-11-24T01:05:09.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-24T10:21:30.000Z","uid":113930,"like":1315,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":104,"replies":[{"pid":"4b4c187e931c3a39880895a444dae17a63eac2eb","tid":1748973,"uid":113930,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-24T01:05:09.000Z","msg":"張建宗一到店，所有喝酒的人便都看着他笑，有的叫道，「張建宗，你在網絡上又添上新潮文了！」他不回答，對櫃里說，「溫兩碗酒，要一碟茴香豆。」便排出九文大錢。他們又故意的高聲嚷道，「你一定又打了會議室的官員了！」張建宗睜大眼睛說，「你怎麼這樣憑空污人清白&hellip;&hellip;」「什麼清白？我前天親眼見你打了鄭家的若驊，吊着打。」張建宗便漲紅了臉，額上的青筋條條綻出，爭辯道，「打狗不能算毆鬥&hellip;&hellip;打狗！&hellip;&hellip;政府高官的事，能算毆鬥麼？」接連便是難懂的話，什麼「完全捏造」，什麼「非常無聊」之類，引得眾人都鬨笑起來：店內外充滿了快活的空氣。"},{"pid":"de35e78aa5f1b841da40db174dc0459d55ed7afc","tid":1748973,"uid":46688,"like":15,"dislike":200,"score":-185,"citedBy":10,"replyTime":"2019-11-24T01:06:16.000Z","msg":"咁撚熟嘅<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n中文篇章？"},{"pid":"bd60ece8f20503e8af4f767779b6b04e9e2d5ac2","tid":1748973,"uid":313203,"like":5,"dislike":63,"score":-58,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-24T01:06:41.000Z","msg":"陽春麵???"},{"pid":"e5e1fb566be9ee83146ef25632e46a00bf6ff718","tid":1748973,"uid":71508,"like":86,"dislike":50,"score":36,"quote":{"pid":"de35e78aa5f1b841da40db174dc0459d55ed7afc","tid":1748973,"uid":46688,"like":15,"dislike":200,"score":-185,"citedBy":10,"replyTime":"2019-11-24T01:06:16.000Z","msg":"咁撚熟嘅<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n中文篇章？"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-24T01:07:01.000Z","msg":"乙孔已"},{"pid":"efaf50228761d6f8965aa02d8231678a85216e5f","tid":1748973,"uid":3355,"like":1,"dislike":44,"score":-43,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-24T01:07:22.000Z","msg":"阿Q<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fa5fa955ffcb0916535bac5a6a77e487c5eaba4c","tid":1748973,"uid":251111,"like":79,"dislike":1,"score":78,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-24T01:07:26.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=