s=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-24T03:58:06.000Z","msg":"你係真心定假膠<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />？"},{"pid":"043ea119a5e27908872b8968edcbd857fceda164","tid":1748973,"uid":5065,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"quote":{"pid":"a52b928d1a069ca7261de3ed117fe1eaf77e053d","tid":1748973,"uid":149607,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-11-24T03:36:27.000Z","msg":"孔乜撚野乙已 <br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">烏大龜呀</span></span><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />話時話佢死撚左去邊"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-24T03:58:22.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">文字支援</span></span><br />\n<br />\n烏大龜一到店，所有喝酒的人便都看著他笑。<br />\n<br />\n有的叫道，「烏大龜，你怎麼又回來學術台了！」<br />\n<br />\n他不回答，對櫃裡說，「溫兩碗酒，要一本教科書。」便排出九文大錢。<br />\n<br />\n他們又故意的高聲嚷道，「你一定又被膠登巴打趕出來了！」<br />\n<br />\n烏大龜睜大眼睛說，「你怎麼這樣憑空污人清白&hellip;&hellip;」<br />\n<br />\n「什麼清白？我前天親眼見你被眾巴打恥笑，吊著打。」<br />\n<br />\n烏大龜便漲紅了臉，額上的青筋條條綻出，爭辯道，「退出不能算趕&hellip;&hellip;退出！&hellip;&hellip;IQ135的ENTJ，還會被趕麼？」<br />\n<br />\n接連便是難懂的話，什麼「Entering university is MK behavior」，什麼「中化考得好都是狗公」之類，引得眾人都鬨笑起來：店內外充滿了快活的空氣。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\nBtw佢都好似有過嚟連登<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"626f7cd3d14c8b615822f30d2344b3b9e1134fbe","tid":1748973,"uid":76548,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-24T03:59:02.000Z","msg":"魯迅<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}